{
  "stem": "3928.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was one of the greatest thing at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I, in the same time, I was concerned about the day there-- Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very much concerned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I used to say this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians made two mistakes during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They let the Russian soldiers see the free world and the free world see the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they behaved like animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They raped every woman from 6 to 60.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, and-- and at the time, you know, the Russians had a big army, which fought with the German, the Vlasov army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know you ever heard about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the Ukrainian Army, who was with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Eisenhower decided to give this back to the Russians, and they were all killed, you know, which I felt no bad-- bad feeling for it, you know, because what they did, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was worried about the Russians because I seen how inhuman they were, even to each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shot each other for a bottle of vodka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I seen them on the street, the Russians, in-- in 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They killed an old man because he wouldn't give up his glove.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, I felt, my god, what kind of a liberation is this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I was very sure, and in my mind and in my thoughts, that nothing like this happen under the American Army, which didn't.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm very sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, so that's the reason I was disappointed of the Yalta agreement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this would-- gave us a chance, in October 15, 1944, to be occupied by the English and American forces and would have been a different story.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the deportation from all these people would not have taken place.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
